<gap reason="lost"/>, Tai Sraca Ta Vraḥ <gap reason="lost"/>;</p>
              <p n="27-32">People from the village of Krva<gap reason="lost"/>, <gap reason="lost"/> 7 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>si</foreign></supplied>, 110 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/> animal keepers <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gvāl</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/>, 10 boys at the age of running <supplied reason="lost"><foreign>si rat</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/> baby boys <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>si pau</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/> without name <gap reason="lost"/>. The <foreign>lvan</foreign> people are <gap reason="lost"/>.</p>
